      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHORTY BOY (1) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 0.8 lengths third over 340m Gunnedah in 19.73. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Top chance in this line up. COOKIE MAN (5) finished second (19.46) two back at Gunnedah but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Has a strong record from box 5, including two wins. Must be included in calculations. FURIOUS (2) is a well performed dog and winner of 19 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (22.63). Solid record here at the distance winning 19 races. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Can measure up. BOMB NOAH (7) is among the chances again if he runs up to the latest effort.",
